snippet.title: Bat Egg Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
It's time for Bat Egg!

Flap, glide, and befriend your way through six zones as a cute bat egg searching for its family in Story Mode. Challenge yourself with Survival Mode's increasing difficulty, or relax with Endless Mode's static difficulty.

Available now for Linux, MacOS (version 10.14 or lower) and Windows at https://cheeseness.itch.io/bat-egg!

For more information, visit http://bategg.twolofbees.com/
